95
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,000
Kedengarannya seperti minuman keras.

96
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,760
Itu Brando, Fei.

97
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,800
merek.

98
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,880
