114
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,416
Xia Liu Yi.

115
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,800
Kamu tampak sangat bahagia hari ini.

116
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:51,760
Saya punya tempat di mana saya merasa aman.

117
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,560
Dan itu membuatku sangat bahagia.

118
00:09:59,986 --> 00:10:02,106
Maka kamu bisa...

119
00:10:03,133 --> 00:10:05,493
