149
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:25,480
- Kamu masuk angin?
- Apakah kamu mudah kedinginan?

150
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,520
Anda akan masuk angin
jika Anda tidak menutupinya di musim panas.

151
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:29,640
Hei, He Chu San...

152
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:35,280
Sudahkah Anda menyikat gigi?

153
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:36,480
Pasta gigi dan sikatnya ada di sana.

154
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,480
Ayo sikat gigimu.

155
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,960
Ayo cepat. Berlangsung.

156
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,160
Chu San.

157
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:49,920
Kalian makan dulu. Aku akan mencari Fei.

158
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:57,960
Masa lalu terasa seperti mimpi sekilas,
dan sulit mengenali perasaanku...

159
00:16:57,960 --> 00:17:02,480
Mengapa kita mengubur nama lama kita
